20 September 2012 Minister in the Presidency responsible for Performance, Monitoring and Evaluation as well as Administration, Collins Chabane will address members of the media on Friday 21 September 2012. The media briefing will take place as follows: Date: Friday, 21 September 2012 Time: 09h00 Venue: 1st Floor Midtown building, corner Madiba and Sisulu Str, Pretoria NB: There will be a video-link to Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Parliament, Cape Town RSVP: Bongiwe Gambu Bongiwe@gcis.gov.za (Pretoria) Cell: 074 055 8388 Mzimasi Ngqelu (Cape Town) E-mail: Mzi@gcis.gov.za Cell: 076 904 3557. Enquiries: Phumla Williams Cell: 083 501 0139 Issued by: Government Communication and Information System (GCIS)